tables.table_schema:

  user_id INT,
  query_text VARCHAR(255),
  query_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  clicked_link BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE SearchQueries (
  query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  query_text TEXT,
  search_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE search_queries (
    query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    query_text VARCHAR(255),
    query_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    search_result_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_behavior (
    behavior_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    behavior_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    behavior_details JSON
);

CREATE TABLE knowledge_discovery (
    discovery_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    discovery_topic VARCHAR(100),
    discovery_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    relevance_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(50),
    user_email VARCHAR(255),
    user_role VARCHAR(50),
    registration_date TIMESTAMP
);
